title: A Flock Of Seagulls - The Story Of A Young Heart
description:
The Story of a Young Heart is the third album by A Flock of Seagulls, released in 1984. It was the last to feature the entire original lineup since guitarist Paul Reynolds left shortly after the album's release.

6."Over My Head" - 3:55
7."Heart of Steel" - 5:45
8."The End" - 3:34
